channel.title: Comments on: Cold War Kids “Something Is Not Right with Me” on Jimmy Kimmel Live 9.19.08

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: I go through phases of loving CWK and alternately finding them intolerable. When I'm in the right mood, I can't get enough of his voice. That was a nice performance.
